description: The ring's dark, ebon metal is set with a single, pulsing gemstone that glows with an inner light, reflecting the movements of the celestial bodies in the sky.
name: Ring of the Eclipse

description: Woven from the finest celestial silks, it shimmers with an otherworldly glow that embodies the power of the dream world.
name: Dreamweaver's Mantle

description: The intricate patterns etched upon its surface are said to be a map of the stars themselves, revealing the secrets of the universe to those who can decipher its secrets.
name: Starlight Amulet

description: It is said that the aurora itself came down from the heavens and imbued the tiara with its power, making it a direct link between the wearer and the sky gods.
name: Aurora's Halo
